review:
As someone with two severely decayed teeth and oral health issues, I knew I needed someone professional yet reliable for my root canal treatment. Having time constraints, I also needed to get it done promptly without further ado.

Not only was Dr. Shruti and her team did a great job on the root canals, crowns, and teeth cleaning but made sure everything was taken care of in flexible time slots.

Her patient-centric educative approach to dentistry helped a lot in making the right choices and alleviated any known fears I had with dentists. Made me comfortable at the dentist's chair as much I would be at home. She'd also check back in between my sessions to ensure everything was on track.

All in all, if you're in town looking for a professional, tailored, and reliable dentistry solution, look no further than Dr. Shruti at ToothWorks. She and her team of specialists are skilled in their trade to get you through even the complex of situations. 

They also use some of the best medical-grade equipment for their treatment so you're left with the best results money can get.

Highly recommended!
